769
01:01:22,779 --> 01:01:26,408
What a night for U. S. pairs skating.
It's extraordinary.

770
01:01:27,150 --> 01:01:30,051
Brian Neuman and Lorie Pekurovsky
into first place.

771
01:01:30,253 --> 01:01:32,653
