01:03:03,480 --> 01:03:05,675
Kate Moseley and Doug Dorsey.

802
01:03:05,882 --> 01:03:08,578
What a performance.
Look at that sit spin.

803
01:03:08,785 --> 01:03:11,913
This crowd knows it's seeing
history in the making.

804
01:03:12,122 --> 01:03:14,852
We're in for a major upset tonight.

805
01:03:33,243 --> 01:03:35,336
oh, yes. That was great skating.

806
01:03:35,545 --> 01:03:37,809
Clean, powerful,
and the crowd just loved it.

807
