of togetherness.

983
01:19:01,837 --> 01:19:04,237
-Spirit.
-Spirit.

984
01:19:04,440 --> 01:19:05,407
Family.

985
01:19:05,608 --> 01:19:09,408
It's-- It's sort of.... It's almost....

986
01:19:09,612 --> 01:19:11,341
-It's almost--
-Orgasmic.

987
01:19:12,047 --> 01:19:13,639
What did she say?

988
01:19:14,717 --> 01:19:16,981
-The Russians.
-The Russians.

989
01:19:17,219 --> 01:19:18,686
Nikolai?

990
01:19:19,355 --> 01:19:20,822
-Nikolai?
-Can we get a photo?

991
01:19:21,023 --> 01:19:23,218
You guys gonna be here a while?

992
01:19:46,749 --> 01:19:48,307
You forgot a button.

993
01:19:48,517 --> 01:19:50,451
No, I like it open.

994
01:19:51,754 --> 01:19:53,449
Well, it looks terrible.

995
01:19:53,656 --> 01:19:55,351
It pulls at my neck.

996
01:19:58,027 --> 01:20:00,393
